premise_source_doc_sentence: Allison Beth Adler  (  born May 30 , 1967  )  is an American television producer and writer .
She is best known as the co-creator of Supergirl , The New Normal and her work on Chuck and Family Guy .
`` Brian Wallows and Peter 's Swallows '' was written by Allison Adler and directed by Dan Povenmire .
